Name: Sony Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphone With Noise Cancelation Black
Short description:
• 40mm Dynamic Drivers
  • Up to 30 Hours Battery with NC On
  • Earcup Touch Controls for Playback/Calls
  • Sony EXTRA BASS Audio Enhancement
  • Works with Sony Headphones Connect App
  • Active Noise-Canceling Technology
  • Supports Google Assistant & Alexa
  • Built-in Mic for Hands-Free Calling
  • Foldable Design + Cushioned Earpads
  • Headphone Cable Included for Wired Use
Description:
With the WH-XB900N Wireless Active Noise-Canceling Over-Ear Headphones from Sony, you can experience your favorite albums or podcasts without the distracting sounds around you. A single microphone takes in the ambient noise, such as traffic noise or people talking, and neutralizes them so all you hear is what you're playing.

The XB900N headphones are engineered to enhance the audio you ear with EXTRA BASS technology. It utilizes a dedicated bass duct on the headphone's housing to give an extra boost to your music, without affecting vocal clarity. The WH-XB900N over-ear headphones are designed to last for up to 30 hours, for all-day entertainment, and can pair to your mobile device via Bluetooth or NFC. Other features include touch controls, digital assistant access, and more.

Convenient and Comfortable Design
These XB900N wireless headphones have soft cushioned earpads to help make them comfortable during extended listening. They are also foldable for easier storage, which helps to make them an ideal fit as your everyday carry headphones.
Hands-Free Calling
A built-in microphone inside the headphones lets you have hands-free phone calls when they are paired with your smartphone. The earcup touch controls let you answer calls and adjust the volume.
Earcup Touch Controls with Quick Attention
The exterior of the right earcup features a built-in touch panel that gives you touch control over volume, music playback, hands-free calls, and the Quick Attention feature. Quick Attention is a useful feature that's enabled by simply placing your hand on the earcup. The volume will automatically lower, allowing you to have a quick conversation or listen to the world around you, all without having to take off your headphones.
Google Assistant & Alexa
The Sony XB900 headphones support both Google Assistant and Alexa digital assistants. Via the headphone's built-in mic, you can ask questions, receive notifications, set reminders, and more.
Sony Headphones Connect App
The XB900N headphones are made to work with Sony's Headphones Connect app, which lets you customize your listening experience via your mobile device. A built-in equalizer lets you adjust sound levels, and Adaptive Sound Control automatically adjusts the ambient sound settings to suit your specific situation

Name: Sony Portable Bluetooth Speaker Black
Short description:
• Stereo Male Audio Cable
  • EXTRA BASS PORTABLE SPEAKER: Its small and compact design with Bluetooth connectivity makes it easy to take anywhere and allows for quick connection
  • BUILT IN MIC AND HANDY STRAP: With the built-in microphone, you taking calls from your smartphone via the speaker is easy. The handy strap comes in a matching color and secures your speaker anywhere
  • PLAYBACK: If you don't have wireless connections, no worry, with the audio input you can connect your music players and enjoy your favorite playlists
Description:
Take your party on the go with the Sony XB01 Extra Bass Portable Bluetooth Speaker. Its small and compact design with Bluetooth connectivity makes it easy to take anywhere and allows for quick connection. No wireless connection? You can still have your party. Just attach your device with an audio cable thanks to the speaker's audio input. Extra Bass technology will get the bass pumping for a rocking party!

Compact Design

The SRS-XB01 features a rounded design and passive radiator that give your tunes deep and punchy sound. Despite its compact size, this speaker delivers a big sound.

Built-in Microphone

Hands-free calling lets you switch quickly from tunes to talking with friends. With the built-in microphone, taking calls from your smartphone via the speaker is easy.

Handy Strap

With the SRS-XB01's handy strap, you're never separated from your favorite tracks. It comes in a matching color and secures your speaker anywhere.

Playback Through Audio Input

No wireless connection? No problem. Plug your music player, such as Walkman or iPod, into the SRS-XB01's audio input and enjoy your favorite playlists.

Bundle Includes:

Sony XB01 Extra Bass Portable Bluetooth Speaker (Black)
Monoprice 10-Feet 3.5mm Stereo Male to 3.5mm Stereo Male Audio Cable (Gold Plated)

Name: Sony Hifi Party Speaker Black
Short description:
• Powerful sound and jet bass booster for room filling bass
  • Multi source playback (Bluetooth/NFC, CD, DVD, USB, etc.) & Easy connection to TV via HDMI
  • Versatile operation modes with gesture control, the Sony | music centre app or voice control via the Fiestable app
  • Multi-colour party lights & Speaker lights that synchronize to the beat
  • Karaoke mode with two mic inputs
Description: Get the party started with Sony’s MHC-V42D sound system. Whatever the occasion, the V42D will fill your space with big volume and booming bass. With angled tweeters spreading sound wider and the JET BASS BOOSTER ensuring bass reaches every corner, wherever you are in the crowd you will hear it clearly and feel it physically. You can also create an immersive festival vibe with the Live Sound Mode which floods your party space with the realistic sound of a live concert. With Near Field Communication (NFC) and Bluetooth, you can connect wirelessly to the high power audio system and get the music going right away. You’ll also benefit from Sony’s LDAC technology, which delivers superior-quality sound over Bluetooth. With different operation modes, you can control your party your way. Gesture Control lets you control the Sony MHC V42D’s functions quickly and easily with just a wave of your hand. The Sony | Music Centre app lets you select the tunes from the dancefloor. You can even connect up to three smartphones at once, so everyone can take turns as the DJ. Voice Control via the Fiestable app allows you to simply say the word and control your music and light display. Light up every corner of the party, even in large spaces with new wider angle multi-coloured party lights and speaker lights that synchronize to the beat, so you can enjoy an authentic nightclub or outdoor festival atmosphere at home. Plus you can get the crowd involved with the Fiestable smartphone app, which turns your smartphone display into your very own party light, mirroring the sound system’s colours and effects. Free your inner pop star with Sony MHCV42D’s karaoke mode. Use the two mic inputs to sing along with friends or even hook up a guitar or bass guitar and rock out. Boost the party and enjoy more powerful sound by connecting multiple speakers via Bluetooth. You can sync up to 50 compatible home audio systems. Not in the mood for dancing? Then throw a movie party. With the HDMI (ARC) output, you can easily hook the sound system up to your TV and enjoy big sound from your top films. The Sony MHC-V42D has even a built-in DVD player, so you can turn your living room into a cinema for you and your friends. Designed for portability, the party sound system lets you take the party on tour. Simply tilt it back on the casters and roll it away to your next stop.

Name: Fitbit Versa 2 Fitness Wristband Stone/Mist Grey
Short description:
• Aluminium Case
  • Track your steps, monitor your heart rate and more!
  • Always-On Display Mode
  • Compatible with Android and iOS Smartphones
  • Water resistant to 50 metres.
Description:
Let your voice be heard with Amazon Alexa
Just press the button and speak to check the weather, set reminders, get on-screen answers to your questions and more using Amazon Alexa.

Sleep better, live better

Focus on your health and fitness

Access your world from your wrist
Stick to your schedule, queue up the perfect playlist, make purchases & more—all from the convenience of your smartwatch.

Know your body better in the Fitbit app.
See the whole picture by using Versa 2 with the free Fitbit app to get the data, motivation and guidance you need to improve.

Name: Fitbit Versa 3 Fitness Wristband Black
Short description:
• Over 6 Days of Battery Life
  • 24/7 Heart Rate Monitoring
  • Stream or Store & Play Music/Podcasts
  • Swimproof Construction
  • SmartTrack Automatic Activity Detection
  • Built-In GPS Tracking
  • Track the Quality of Your Sleep
  • All-Day Activity Tracking
  • Female Health Tracking
  • Call, Text & App Notifications
Description:
More easily track your outdoor exercises with the Versa 3 GPS Smartwatch from Fitbit Made for multi-day tracking the Versa 3 features over 6 days of battery life and utilizes built-in GPS tracking, so you don't need to bring your smartphone along on a run, hike, or while biking. The GPS function tracks both your pack and distance. The Versa 3 handles a variety of exercises and basic 24/7 activity tracking of steps, distance, and calories burned. You can choose from over 20 exercises to track, or use SmartTrack, where the Versa 3 will automatically detect the exercise and track it for you.

Your health is intimately linked with how effective you are in reaching your fitness goals. With the Versa 3, you get 24/7 heart rate monitors that earns you Active Zone Minutes when reaching target heart rate zones. You can even keep tabs on your sleep quality by wearing it through the night. You can learn how well you've slept, get an overall sleep score, and learn about sleep trends that you can adjust for a better night's rest. All of these features and more are can be controlled via the Versa 3's built-in bright OLED display.

Manage Your Music
When you do bring your smartphone with you, you can use the Versa 3's built-in apps to manage a variety of audio experiences to keep you motivated. Access Spotify, download Pandora stations, or play Deezer playlists.

Notifications & Assistants
Pairing with iOS and Android devices gives you additional practical features to keep you connected to the outside world. Receive incoming calls, texts, and app notifications. You can also perform functions and get information using voice commands. The Versa 3 supports both Google Assistant and Alexa digital assistants.

Health Features
Uses PurePulse 2.0 to record your resting heart rate
Track calories burned, view heart rate trends and cardio fitness levels in the Fitbit app
See how much light, deep, and REM sleep you get
Smart Wake gives you a quiet vibration to more peacefully wake you
Sleep Mode disables notifications to help you sleep better
Personalized 2- and 5-minute guided breathing sessions based on your heart rate
Women can track menstrual cycles, record symptoms, and more
Personalized reminders nudge you to move more, keep to a regular sleep schedule, take 250 steps per hour, and more

Fitness Features
Use the Fitbit app to view a workout intensity map, seeing heart rate zones reached throughout your route
All-day activity tracking of steps, distance, floors climbed, active minutes, and calories burned
Wear the Versa 3 in the pool with up to 164' of water resistance
An in-app cardio fitness score gives you a better idea of your personal fitness level

Smart Features
Receive call, text, and app notifications
Android users can send quick replies to message from the Versa 3
Use the Fitbit app and Fitbit Pay to pay for items with a tap of your watch
Choose from hundreds of apps that cover many aspects of your daily life, such as Uber, United Airlines, TRX, and more
Do Not Disturb mode mutes calls, texts, calendar and app notifications

General Features
Get up to 24 hours of power in just 12 minutes with fast charging
The always-on display function lets you monitor your stats with just a glance
Customize the display with hundreds of clock face options online
Store up to 5 clock faces on the Versa 3
Compatible with the Fitbit app for viewing stats, taking part in group challenges, and much more
Categories: Smart Watches, Smart Watches > Smart Watches

Name: Belkin Powerhouse Charging Dock Duo Black
Short description:
• Back panel supports iPhone while charging
  • Includes a built-in Lightning connector for iPhone
  • Holds Apple Watch safely above surface
  • Versa Case- red dial raises/lowers adjustable case-friendly Lightning connector to fit most cases
  • Includes a built-in Magnetic Charging Module for Apple Watch
Description: Charge and display your Apple Watch and iPhone simultaneously with the 2-in-1 Powerhouse Charge Dock for Apple Watch plus iPhone. With a Magnetic Charging Module for the Apple Watch built into the dock, your Apple Watch aligns magnetically and begins charging instantly. The dock also features a built-in Versa Case Lightning connector to charge your iPhone, that can be adjusted to fit almost any case. Engineered to charge both devices at the fastest possible speed, the dock also elevates them for safety and visibility while they charge.

Name: Belkin 10000Mah Multi-Port Power Bank 15W White
Short description:
• 10,000mAh Battery Capacity
  • 1 x USB Type-C Input & Output
  • Up to 15W of Power Output
  • Portable Design
  • 6" USB Type-A to Type-C Cable Included
  • 2 x USB Type-A Output
  • 1 x Micro-USB Input
  • Charge up to Three Devices at Once
  • LED Indicator
Description:
Keep your gear juiced up on the go with the 10,000mAh Boost Charge Multi-Port Power Bank in white from Belkin. Designed to charge multiple devices at once, this power bank features two USB Type-A outputs, a USB Type-C input and output, and a micro-USB input. The 10,000mAh battery capacity and up to 15W of power delivery ensure your smartphone or other devices stay ready for use. An LED indicator alerts you to the charging status, and the Boost Charge Multi-Port is less than 4" on its longest side, making for easy transport. This power bank comes with a 6" USB Type-A to Type-C charging cable.

You Have the Power
The 10,000mAh Belkin Boost Charge Multi-Port provides up to 36 hours of battery life to your smartphone. Connect your device via USB Type-C or A, and you'll be able to chat, FaceTime, and use apps longer without having to worry about losing your charge.
Versatile Power
This power bank provides up to 15W of power when using the USB Type-C port, or when using all three ports. Get up to 12W of power when using a single USB Type-A port, or up to 12W shared when using both Type-A ports.

Name: Belkin Power Pocket 15000Mah With 2 Usb Ports Black
Short description:
• Compact and thin design for portability
  • 6 inch Micro-USB cable recharges the battery
  • 4 LED indicators show battery power level
  • Lightweight, efficient, Polymer cells
  • Durable plastic casing
Description:
Stay charged anywhere with the Belkin Pocket Power Bank 15000mAh w/ Micro USB Black that fits easily into your bag.

Two universal USB-A ports deliver up to 3.4A of total power to quickly and safely charge devices like smartphones, smartwatches, fitness bands, headphones, speakers and more.

Dual USB ports allow you to charge two devices at the same time, so you never have to choose between using your phone or tablet, camera or speakers, or anything else you need.

A 5V 2.0A input allows the power bank to recharge quickly between uses, so you can keep moving. 15,000 mAh recharges a smartphone to provide 105 additional hours of video playback.

Belkin batteries include sensors to monitor heat, voltage and circuitry so the device won’t overheat or surge. Excess heat, voltage fluctuation or circuit abnormalities activate an override that immediately shuts the battery down and keeps your devices safe.

Name: Belkin Usb 2.0 Travel Hub White
Short description:
• Adds four additional USB ports to your computer
  • Built-in cable management
  • Plug and play; no drivers required
  • Data transfer speeds of up to 480Mbps
  • Mac/PC compatible
Description: Enjoy the convenience of connecting four devices to a single USB hub with the this Belkin 4 port hub USB. You can connect various PC accessories to your PC or laptop and even charge multiple smartphones via this USB hub. It comes with an inbuilt plug-and-play functionality that allows you to connect and access USB devices without installing any software. Connect devices like flash drives or hard drives to this 4 port mini hub USB and transfer data at a high speeds of up to 480mbps.\n\nThis Belkin 4 port USB 2.0 hub is compatible with both 1.1 and 2.0 USB connectors, giving you the flexibility to connect myriad USB devices. Compact and lightweight, you can easily tuck it in your laptop bag or your satchel and get a move on. With this easy and multi-connectivity option, you can reduce the clutter of USB cables on your desktop too. With no extra power-supply requirement, this Belkin 4 port USB 2.0 hub is a handy accessory. Moreover, this ultra mini hub USB features a light indicator that flashes to signal connectivity.

Name: Belkin Usb-C To Vga Adapter Black
Short description:
• USB-C to VGA connectivity
  • USB-C Male and VGA Female
  • 15cm length
Description:
AS SEEN ON SCREEN
From the screen of your USB-C-enabled device straight to your projector or monitor, smoothly and effortlessly. The USB-C to VGA Adapter is 15cm of finely tuned USB-C cable designed and tested by Belkin, allowing a seamless connection from any compatible USB-C device to your legacy projector, TV or monitor. Whether it’s sharing content at work, or transitioning new tech into your home office, it’s the ideal solution for your USB-C enabled device.

MADE FOR:
USB-C devices

Name: Belkin 3.5mm Audio + Usb-C Charge Adapter Black
Short description:
• Has a 3.5mm audio jack, allowing you to listen to your favourite songs, podcasts, and audiobooks with ease
  • Plastic-encased connectors and TPE-jacketed cable for great durability against accidental pulls, yanks, and tugs
Description: The Belkin RockStar 3.5mm Audio + USB-C Charge Adapter is a handy solution for adding a 3.5mm headphone/speaker jack to your USB-C enabled device to cater to your charging and audio playback needs.

Name: Belkin Usb-C To Gigabit Ethernet 60W Black
Short description:
• Plug-and-play USB-C to Ethernet adapter that allows for device charging
  • Charge while your device is in use with pass-through power up to 60W
  • Supports Ethernet speeds up to 1000 Mbps
  • Compatible with Mac and Windows laptops and other USB-C devices
  • Compatible devices: Any USB-C devices
Description:
Do It All Through One Port
Belkin USB-C to Ethernet + Charge Adapter
This USB-C to Ethernet + Charge Adapter provides convenient access to fast and reliable Internet connection through a gigabit Ethernet port and allows for USB Power Delivery at the same time. It's a plug-and-play adapter that works universally with Mac and Windows laptops and other USB-C devices.

Don't Stop to Charge
Connect and stay powered while surfing the Internet or transferring data. Pass-through Power Delivery of up to 60W allows you to stay charged while you work using a single USB-C port.

Reliable Ethernet Connection
Connect with confidence where wireless connectivity is inconsistent or even non-existent. This adapter provides access to a reliable Internet connection up to gigabit speeds up to 1000 Mbps for confidently transferring large files or hosting a web conference call without interruption.

Name: Belkin Lightning Audio + Charge Rockstar White
Short description:
• Metal shield provides structure to protect delicate circuit board
  • Shield prevents electro-magnetic interference from circuit board affecting phone signal and wifi
  • Electrical firmware design makes connectors interchangeable for audio and charging
  • MFi certified Lightning connectors carry audio and power
  • Jacket and strain relief made from flexible, soft touch, environmentally friendly TPE
Description:
DUAL FUNCTIONALITY
12W pass-through charging powers up the iPhone/iPad at maximum speed. So whether you’re listening to music, watching videos, using navigation, or taking calls, you can charge anywhere

AUDIO QUALITY
The Lightning Audio + Charge RockStar supports up to 24bit 48kHz lossless output, and is compatible with the full ecosystem of Lightning Audio headphones. The RockStar will also support the higher power delivery required by premium or professional standard Lightning Audio headphones to deliver superior noise cancellation without the need for batteries or an additional power supply.

"MADE FOR IPHONE" "MADE FOR IPAD"
“Made for iPhone” and “Made for iPad” mean that an electronic accessory has been designed to connect specifically to iPhone or iPad respectively, and has been certified by the developer to meet Apple specifications.

At A Glance:
Dual functionality to listen to Lightning Audio and charge at the same time

Supports pass-through charging up to 12W for iPhone and iPad

Supports up to 48 kHz, 24-bit audio output

Compatible with Lightning Audio headphones† and the Apple Lightning to 3.5 mm Headphone Jack Adapter

Supports remote control and microphone from Lightning Audio headphones

Works with Apple iPhone 7 Smart Battery Case

Made for iPhone + iPad

Name: Fitbit Sense Fitness Wristband Heart Rate Tracker White/Gold
Short description:
• Up to 6 Days of Battery Life
  • Heart Rate Monitoring
  • Built-In AMOLED Display
  • Swimproof Construction
  • SmartTrack Automatic Activity Detection
  • Built-In GPS Tracking
  • On-Wrist Skin Temperature Sensor
  • Stress Detection & Tracking
  • Female Health Tracking
  • Call, Text & App Notifications
Description:
Track your health and fitness with the Sense GPS Smartwatch from Fitbit. It's essential to maintain good health to better achieve your fitness goals, which is why Fitbit incorporates a variety of health tracking options in the Sense smartwatch. Features like an on-wrist EDA scan app to detect electrodermal activity. This tracks your stress and graphs it, letting you track trends and change habits to reduce stress. You also get on-wrist heart rate monitoring with an ECG app to help assess a possible AFib condition, SpO2, a skin temperature sensor, and sleep tracking.

Name: JBL QUANTUM200 Wired Over Ear Gaming Headset Black
Description:
In competitive gaming, sound is survival, and JBL knows great sound: From the thrill of tracking enemies in FPS games, to engaging in epic MOBA battles, the JBL Quantum 200 amplifies every victory on PC, Mac, Xbox, PS4 and Nintendo Switch.

Features JBL Quantum Sound Signature which is engineered for accuracy and delivers immersive gaming audio for a competitive edge, so users never have to miss a step, shot or jump during gameplay

JBL Quantum 200 gaming headset incorporates a flip-up boom microphone with echo cancelling technology, allowing users to focus on their teammates' voice rather than background noise, for crystal clear communication.

Memory foam ear cushions on the JBL Quantum 200 gaming headset are covered in soft PU leather, providing comfort for marathon sessions, plus 3.5 millimeter and PC splitter connections for multi-platform gaming on PC, Mac, Xbox, PS4 and Nintendo Switch.

Items delivered: JBL Quantum 200 wired over ear gaming headset with flip-up boom mic in black, compatible with PC, Mac, Xbox, PlayStation, Nintendo Switch, mobile and VR.

Name: Beats Flex All-Day Wireless Earphones Yellow
Short description:
• Magnetic earbuds with Auto-Play/Pause
  • Custom acoustic platform delivers premium sound with accurate bass and low distortion
  • Built-in microphone with wind reduction for elevated voice clarity
  • Up to 12 hours of listening time
  • All-day comfort with Flex-Form cable and four ear tip options
  • Powered by the Apple W1 chip for seamless connectivity
  • Audio Sharing lets you wirelessly share audio with another pair of Beats headphones or AirPods
  • 10-minute Fast Fuel charging gives 1.5 hours of playback
  • Class 1 Bluetooth® for extended range and fewer dropouts
  • On-device controls for volume, track and call controls located on the left side of neckband housing
  • Power button located on the right side of neckband housing
Description: Flex All Day In your ears or around your neck, Beats Flex are as versatile as the life you lead. Whether you’re listening to music, taking calls, or scrolling your social feed, you’ll always be ready for what’s next. Magnetic earbuds make listening that much easier by automatically playing music when they’re in your ears and pausing when they’re attached around your neck. The Flex-Form cable provides all-day comfort with durable Nitinol construction while four eartip options offer a personalized fit. And when you’re not wearing them, the magnetic earbuds keep Beats Flex tangle-free as they easily coil up into your pocket or purse. Driven by Premium Sound Beats Flex employs a dual-chamber acoustic design and a proprietary layered driver to achieve outstanding stereo separation with rich and precise bass response. Laser cut micro-venting provides ear pressure relief, and the optimized driver angle ensures clear, crisp sound. An advanced digital processor fine-tunes your audio for an accurate and emotive listening experience. The result — rich, powerful sound that keeps you inspired all day long.

  • Power button located on the right side of neckband housing
Description: Flex All Day In your ears or around your neck, Beats Flex are as versatile as the life you lead. Whether you’re listening to music, taking calls, or scrolling your social feed, you’ll always be ready for what’s next. Magnetic earbuds make listening that much easier by automatically playing music when they’re in your ears and pausing when they’re attached around your neck. The Flex-Form cable provides all-day comfort with durable Nitinol construction while four eartip options offer a personalized fit. And when you’re not wearing them, the magnetic earbuds keep Beats Flex tangle-free as they easily coil up into your pocket or purse. Driven by Premium Sound Beats Flex employs a dual-chamber acoustic design and a proprietary layered driver to achieve outstanding stereo separation with rich and precise bass response. Laser cut micro-venting provides ear pressure relief, and the optimized driver angle ensures clear, crisp sound. An advanced digital processor fine-tunes your audio for an accurate and emotive listening experience. The result — rich, powerful sound that keeps you inspired all day long.

Either bud or both, immediately connected

Thanks to Fast Pair enabled by Google, the JBL LIVE FREE NC+ TWS are connected to your Android device the second you flip the case open. Name: Apple AirTag - Pack of 1 White
Short description:
• AirTags use audible beeps through the built-in speaker when in Bluetooth range to help you locate the device they are attached to
  • They offer NFC and Bluetooth LE connectivity, apart from featuring an accelerometer
  • The AirTags also feature Siri support and a claimed one year of battery life
  • AirTag is an easy way to keep track of your stuff
  • Attach one to your keys, slip another one in your backpack
Description: AirTag is a super-easy way to keep track of your stuff. Attach one to your keys, slip another in your backpack. And just like that, they're on your radar in the Find My app, where you can also track down your Apple devices and keep up with friends and family. Misplacing something like your wallet doesn't have to be a big deal when it has AirTag attached. You can play a sound on the built-in speaker by going to the new Items tab in the Find My app, or say "Hey Siri, find my wallet". If it's hiding nearby, like under the couch or in the next room, just follow the sound and your search is over. Each AirTag is equipped with the Apple-designed U1 chip using Ultra Wideband technology, enabling Precision Finding5 for iPhone 11 and iPhone 12 users. This advanced technology can more accurately determine the distance and direction to a lost AirTag when it is in range. As a user moves, Precision Finding fuses input from the camera, ARKit, accelerometer, and gyroscope, and then will guide them to AirTag using a combination of sound, haptics, and visual feedback. Users can also place AirTag into Lost Mode and be notified when it is in range or has been located by the vast Find My network. If a lost AirTag is found by someone, they can tap it using their iPhone or any NFC-capable device and be taken to a website that will display a contact phone number for the owner, if they have provided one. AirTag is also designed with a set of proactive features that discourage unwanted tracking, an industry first. Bluetooth signal identifiers transmitted by AirTag rotate frequently to prevent unwanted location tracking. iOS devices can also detect an AirTag that isn’t with its owner, and notify the user if an unknown AirTag is seen to be traveling with them from place to place over time. And even if users don’t have an iOS device, an AirTag separated from its owner for an extended period of time will play a sound when moved to draw attention to it. If a user detects an unknown AirTag, they can tap it with their iPhone or NFC-capable device and instructions will guide them to disable the unknown AirTag.

Apple Watch Nike SE-40 mm GPS with Nike Sport Band Silver
Short description:
• Retina LTPO OLED Display
  • Digital Crown With Haptic Feedback
  • Always-On Altimeter
  • Up To 1000 Nits (When Screen Is Active)
  • Second-Generation Optical Heart Sensor
  • Fall Detection
  • Swim Proof
  • Exclusive Nike Watch Faces
  • Ion-X Glass
  • Bluetooth 5.0
  • Silver Aluminum Case With Platinum Sport Band Finish
Description:
Stay safe, active, and healthy with the Apple Watch Nike SE. The SE sports the same bright LTPO OLED Retina display as the Series 6, giving you a bright screen you can view at a glance, even in bright sunlight. On it, you can view all of your fitness metrics, health stats, and mobile notifications. When it comes to health, the SE's optical heart rate monitor can give you indicators of a possible medical condition with notifications for high or low heart rates, as well as irregular rhythms. Even healthy habits are supported, such as hand-washing detection, which displays a 20-second animated countdown as you scrub.

Fitness is a large part of staying healthy, and the Apple Watch SE has a variety of ways to assist you in reaching your goals. Activity Rings displays three rings that correspond to movement, exercise, and standing. Stay mobile throughout the day to hit new personal bests as you close the rings. You can also choose from a variety of workouts, such as running, swimming, yoga, cycling, and more; with the watch recording and tracking their specific metrics. Whether inside or outdoors, the SE can guide you via GPS and even provide continuous elevation updates on screen.

As you move, choose from a variety of music, podcasts, and audiobooks to entertain and motivate you. For added fun, share your activity rings with friends and challenge them to 7-day activity competitions. Throughout the day, the Apple Watch SE keeps you connected with the world around you. When paired with your iPhone, you can make calls and send texts directly from your wrist, navigate your surroundings with Maps, buy items with Apple Pay, and use your voice to interact with Siri. Made to last in almost any kind of weather, the Apple Watch SE is water-resistant up to 164'. Use its 32GB of built-in storage for apps, watch faces, music, and more.

Run Smarter & Safer With Nike

Utilizing the Nike Run Club app and new modular complications, this Nike model of the Series 6 lets you optimize your runs. Select a Featured Run for the day and start it at any time. As you run, you can monitor metrics, such as cadence, average pace, and total miles. When you're finished running, new unlocked Streak icons give you bragging rights when you meet your weekly mile goals. You can view your monthly mile totals as well as use the Pace Graph complication for a more detailed view of your progress. For additional safety while running, enable Nike Twilight Mode to fill the watch face with a solid color so you can be more visible as you go.

Sleep Monitoring

The Sleep app works with the Apple Watch to track sleep trends, providing you with data and metrics to allow you to get a better night's rest.

Wellness

General wellness can affect not just your health, but also your ability or motivation to exercise. The Apple Watch SE provides a variety of indicators to ensure you're in the best possible condition for success.

Receive a gentle tap to notify you when ambient noise levels are too high

Track your menstrual cycle from your wrist

Use the Breath app to perform breathing exercises to center yourself and calm your heart rate

Apple Fitness+

A free 3-month trial of Apple Fitness+ is included with the Apple Watch SE. Fitness+ gives you access to knowledgeable trainers for a more focused workout, and metrics can be shared between Apple devices, including an iPhone, iPad, and Apple TV.

Watch Faces

A wide range of watch faces are available for the SE watch, including hobby-based faces that provide essential information for specific activities. You can also select from faces that express your personality, heritage, or style. Some watch faces include:

  • Waterspeed: Surfing forecasts and conditions from Dawn Patrol, plus data for sailing, kayaking, and more
  • SolarWatch & NightSky: See a visualization of the day/night cycle and display stargazing conditions
  • CARROT Weather: Weather forecasts, humidity, barometric pressure, and more
  • Lumy: Photographers can track sunrises, sunsets, lighting conditions, and weather

Family Setup

Allow members of your family to use an Apple Watch SE, even if they don't own an iPhone. All you need is one iPhone to pair everyone's watches. Once paired, the iPhone can manage the watches and everyone can stay in touch via phone, text, or walkie-talkie. Each watch can also play music, find apps, and utilize integrated fitness tracking, such as Activity Rings.

Fall Detection

The Apple Watch SE uses an accelerometer and gyroscope to detect whether you've fallen. If a fall occurs, the Apple Watch delivers an on-screen prompt where you can swipe to have it call emergency services or dismiss it. After 60 seconds of unresponsiveness, the SE will place the call automatically and send a message to your emergency contacts.

Emergency SOS

Emergency SOS allows you to quickly get help. It calls 911, notifies your emergency contacts, sends your current location, and displays your Medical ID badge on the screen for emergency personnel.

Activity Rings

Three activity rings on the Apple Watch SE are designed to help you measure all of the ways you move throughout the day. As you move, each ring begins to close, giving you additional motivation to close your rings and increase mobility.

  • Move: The Move ring tracks the active calories you burn. Active calories are the ones you burn through all kinds of movement, from taking the stairs at work to playing with the kids.
  • Exercise: The Exercise ring shows you how many minutes of brisk activity you've done, whether you're working out or just moving at a fast pace.
  • Stand: Sitting too much has the potential to contribute to health problems over time. This ring is designed to keep track of the amount of times you stand throughout the day.

  • Move: The Move ring tracks the active calories you burn. Active calories are the ones you burn through all kinds of movement, from taking the stairs at work to playing with the kids.
  • Exercise: The Exercise ring shows you how many minutes of brisk activity you’ve done, whether you’re working out or just moving at a fast pace.
  • Stand: Sitting too much has the potential to contribute to health problems over time. This ring is designed to keep track of the amount of times you stand throughout the day.

Short description:
• 32GB Capacity
  • Ion-X Glass Display
  • Blood Oxygen App
  • Always-On Altimeter
  • Sleep Tracking
  • Always-On Retina LTPO OLED Display
  • Electrical Heart Sensor
  • S6 SiP With 64-bit Dual-Core Processor
  • Digital Crown With Haptic Feedback
  • Up To 18 Hours Battery Life
  • Water Resistant Up To 50 Meters
  • Fall Detection Enabled
  • Emergency SOS
  • Silver Case And Pure Platinum/Black Nike Sport Band Finish
Description:
Apple Watch Series 6 is the most advanced Apple Watch ever, with breakthrough health technologies to help you live better and even more features to keep you active, healthy, and connected. With a new Blood Oxygen app that measures the oxygen in your blood, you can get greater insight into your wellness anytime, anywhere, directly from your wrist. Meet your sleep goals with sleep tracking. Take your activity to new heights with the always-on altimeter and expanded workout types. With these powerful features and more, Apple Watch Series 6 is there for you like never before. Blood Oxygen app
  • A sensor and app measure the oxygen saturation of your blood, an important indication of how well your body is absorbing oxygen
  • Just remain still for 15 seconds to measure your blood oxygen—results appear on your watch and in the Health app on iPhone
  • Series 6 takes periodic readings in the background, even while you’re sleeping, recording your blood oxygen trends over time
Advanced Performance
  • Redesigned S6 System in Package delivers even greater performance, so apps launch up to 20 percent faster than on Series 5
  • Always-On Retina display is up to 2.5 times brighter outdoors when your wrist is down than Series 5, making it easier to see in bright light
Always-on altimeter
  • 18-hour, all-day battery life with longer workouts and more audio playback time, plus faster charging with 0 percent to 100 percent charge in just 1.5 hours
    • Get real-time elevation readings throughout the day with minimal impact to battery life
    • See your elevation change foot-by-foot right on your watch face with the Elevation complication—whether you’re running a trail or taking the stairs
    Heart health
    • Electrodes in the Digital Crown and the back crystal work with the ECG app to read your heart’s electrical signals and generate an electrocardiogram
    • Apple Watch can check your heart rhythm in the background and alert you to an irregular rhythm that appears to be atrial fibrillation (AFib)
    • With the optical heart sensor, you can check your heart rate at any time in the Heart Rate app—and see your resting, walking, and workout recovery heart rates
    • Heart rate notifications tell you if your heart rate is above or below a certain number of beats per minute
    • With Low Cardio Fitness (coming later this year), Apple Watch notifies you if your cardiorespiratory fitness level, or VO2 max, falls into a lower range —an important measure of your overall health
    Additional health features
    • Automatic handwashing detection starts a 20-second countdown and features reminders to help you build healthy habits
    • The Noise app alerts you when decibel levels in your environment reach a point that could harm your hearing
    Safety
    • With fall detection enabled, Apple Watch can detect hard falls, initiate a call to emergency services, and alert your emergency contacts
    • With Emergency SOS, you can call local emergency services and notify your emergency contacts just by holding down the side button
    Sleep tracking
    • The Sleep app helps you meet your sleep goals, go to bed on time, and even start a pre-bedtime routine with Wind Down
    • Sleep Mode helps minimize distractions from notifications, and you can set haptic alarms to wake gently without disturbing anyone around you
    • Accelerometer tracks how long you sleep and shows two-week trends
    New workout types
    • Get the most accurate calorie credit for your activity with workouts like Dance, Core Training, Functional Strength Training, and Cooldown
    Cases and finishes
    • Available in silver and space gray aluminum
    • Apple Watch Series 6 works with all Apple Watch bands
    Nike
    • Nike models have updated band colors and a Nike Compact face with space for multiple complications from the Nike Run Club app, like Streaks and Pace
    Essential additions
    • AppleCare+ for Apple Watch, Apple Music,6 AirPods, Apple Watch Magnetic Charging Dock, additional Apple Watch bands

Name: Apple AirPods Max Pink with Red Headband
Short description:
• Active Noise Cancellation
  • Knit Mesh Canopy Reduces Pressure
  • Support for Siri Personal Assistant
  • On-Head Detection for Auto Play/Pause
  • Soft Memory Foam Earcups
  • Up to 20 Hours of Playback
  • 3 Mics with Beamforming for Clear Calls
  • Transparency Mode Lets Sound Back In
  • Digital Crown Control for Audio & Siri
  • Smart Case Included
Description:
Combining premium materials and advanced audio technology, the sky blue Apple AirPods Max wireless over-ear headphones are a comfortable way to immerse yourself in your favorite audio. They are made to rest lightly on your head and ears with a breathable knit mesh canopy and mesh textile-wrapped memory foam earcups. Inside, dynamic drivers with dual neodymium ring magnets work to deliver clear sound with deep bass. Active noise cancellation technology enhances this passive immersion by actively neutralizing ambient sounds with anti-noise.

The AirPods Max are ideal for any kind of audio entertainment, but with movies, they make you feel like you're part of the action. This is due to the Airpods Max's use of spatial audio and dynamic head tracking to better simulate audio that surrounds you. You can use them with a variety of Bluetooth-compatible Apple devices, but when paired with an iPhone, you can utilize three built-in microphones and beamforming technology to make clear hands-free calls or interact with Siri. You can do all of this and more for up to 20 hours on a full charge.

Active Noise Cancellation
Apple uses six outward-facing microphones to measure distracting ambient sounds, and then neutralizes it with anti-noise. This is meant to isolate you with only the audio you want to hear. During playback two additional inward-facing microphones measure what you're hearing, and then use adaptive EQ to adjust frequencies for a consistent experience and faithful audio reproduction.

Transparency Mode
When active noise cancelling mode is on, you can easily chat with others or listen in on your surroundings without taking off your AirPods Max. Simply press the dedicated noise control button to active transparency mode, and let outside sounds back in.
Save Battery Life with a Smart Case
Included with the Airpods Max is Apple's Smart Case, which conveniently stores the headphones and puts them into an ultra-low-power state to preserve battery life.
Built for Comfort
Over-ear headphones can be cumbersome to wear for long periods of time, which is why Apple redesigned the headband of the AirPods Max to incorporate a breathable knit mesh canopy. This canopy is designed to optimally distribute the weight of the headphones to reduce on-head pressure. It's connected to two earcups that sport a mesh textile-wrapped memory foam for pillow-like softness.

Each anodized aluminum earcup rotates independently to further balance pressure and improve comfort. Telescoping arms extend smoothly and stay in place to ensure the earcups maintain a precise fit. The entire AirPods Max durable stainless steel frame is wrapped in a soft-touch material to give them a premium look and feel.

Hands-Free Calls & Siri
The sounds around you can not only distract you as you listen, but they can ruin conversations as well. When paired with an iPhone for hands-free calling, the AirPods Max uses three microphones and beamforming technology to focus on your voice and ensure that it's transmitted clearly.

Siri
With the AirPods Max, Siri is always on and ready to help. Get directions, weather forecasts, listen to your schedule, and more. Siri will even speak incoming messages to you when they arrive with the Announce Messages feature. You can then tell Siri to respond via voice command.

On-Head Detection
Sensors built into the AirPods Max will detect when they are removed and will automatically pause your audio. Audio will automatically resume when the AirPods Max detect that you've placed them back on your head.

Additional Features
Quick charging for five minutes gives the AirPods Max up to 1.5 hours of playback
Digital crown control for volume, tracks, phone, and Siri
Apple-designed H1 chip in each earcup to control active noise cancellation, spatial audio, and more
Seamlessly switch between iPhone, iPad & Mac without disrupting audio or conversations
Share streaming audio between two sets of AirPods when paired with an iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, or Apple TV

Name: Apple Homepod Mini Smart Speaker Space Gray
Short description:
• Full-Range Driver
  • Built-In Siri
  • Wi-Fi & Bluetooth 5.0 Connectivity
  • Dual Passive Radiators
  • Four-Microphone Array for Far-Field Siri
  • Touch Surface
Description:
Control all your compatible Apple devices, talk to family members in other rooms, and enjoy full Siri functionality with the space gray Apple HomePod mini. It connects to your wireless network to provide control of, and access to, all of your HomeKit-compatible devices. It will play music, check the weather and traffic, tell you sports scores, control your compatible smart home equipment, and more with Siri. Using a far-field four-microphone array, the HomePod mini can perform the requested task in an instant. Siri can be activated with the words "Hey Siri" or by touching and holding the touch surface. With Siri, a variety of features work across the HomePod mini and other compatible devices for full integration into your Apple ecosystem.

360° Audio
At just 3.3" tall, the HomePod mini takes up minimal space and is designed to fill the room with 360° audio for enhanced sound from nearly any angle. The acoustic waveguide directs sound out the bottom of the speaker to create the 360° audio field for consistent audio virtually everywhere in the room.

Computational Audio
The Apple S5 chip enables computational audio, which processes complex algorithms in real time to help produce balanced, fine-tuned sound at nearly any volume and provide the full, detailed tones of a larger speaker without missing your voice commands. The full-range driver uses a powerful neodymium magnet to deliver deep bass and crisp high frequencies.

Bass Extension
The force-canceling passive radiators help extend the bass response of the HomePod mini.

Noise Cancellation
Four microphones work together to help cancel noise and listen for your "Hey Siri" command, so even if your environment is loud, you don't have to turn the volume down or move closer to the speaker to be heard.

Designed to Fit Nearly Anywhere
The HomePod mini is wrapped in a seamless mesh fabric that's virtually transparent to the sound passing through it. A backlit touch surface on the top provides quick touch control.

Expandable Design
With multiple HomePod mini or AirPlay 2-compatible speakers placed around the house, you can have a connected sound system for your whole home. Ask Siri to play one song everywhere or a different song in each room. The speaker also works with the HomePod for multiroom audio and features like Intercom.

Stereo Pairing
If you want to take the sound experience even further, you can connect two HomePod mini speakers in the same room to create a stereo pair for discrete left and right channels and a more immersive soundstage.

Siri Voice Assistant
Whether you need a hand with various everyday tasks, want control over your smart home accessories, or want to hear your favorite song, you can just ask Siri. Siri can recognize the voices of up to six different family members on the HomePod mini and create a personalized experience for each person, so everyone hears their own music when they ask for it. With Personal Requests, Siri can recognize a particular voice and relay that person's information from iPhone apps like Messages, Calendar, Reminders, and Contacts.

Intercom Spreads the Word
With more than one HomePod in the house, you can communicate with your family members using the Intercom function. Ask Siri to send your message to the whole house, or to individual rooms, and everyone can respond. Intercom also works with your other compatible Apple devices, so you can send and receive messages through CarPlay while you're driving, on your AirPods during a workout, or with your Apple Watch while you're running errands.

Designed for Easy Connection, Setup, and Control
Getting set up and staying connected from anywhere is designed to be easy with the Home app and the HomePod mini. When you set it up, it's automatically added to the Home app, and you can instantly control any of your HomeKit devices with just your voice. The HomePod mini can also act as a home hub, letting you control your HomeKit accessories remotely, see a live view from the front door, close your garage door, and lock or unlock doors through the Home app.

Engineered to Protect Your Privacy
The HomePod mini only listens for "Hey Siri," so you can speak freely knowing that nothing you say is sent out of your home until you activate Siri, whether with a touch or with the words, "Hey Siri." When you ask Siri something, your request is associated with a random identifier, not your Apple ID. With HomeKit Secure Video support, the HomePod mini can analyze the feeds of your supported video cameras, detecting the presence of people and recognizing familiar faces, pets, and cars. All the video processing is done on the device before it's sent via end-to-end encryption to the iCloud, so your recordings are only seen by you and those you share them with, not Apple. The speaker also works with your iPhone for requests like hearing your messages or notes, so they're completed on the device without revealing the information to Apple.

Works with Your Apple Devices
Pick up an incoming call from your iPhone, listen to music on your Mac, or upgrade your TV experience by taking the sound from your Apple TV, all through the HomePod mini. You can switch audio playback from the HomePod mini to your iPhone by simply bringing your iPhone close to the speaker. Following a scheduled future firmware update, you'll feel the connection between your iPhone and the HomePod mini via haptic feedback, as well as personalized listening suggestions via your iPhone when you hold it near the HomePod mini, providing instant control without having to unlock your iPhone.

Supported Audio Sources
Apple Music, iTunes music purchases, iCloud Music Library with an Apple Music or iTunes Match subscription, third-party music services, Apple Music Radio or episodes on demand, radio stations from TuneIn, iHeartRadio, and Radio.com, Apple Podcasts, News briefings, and content streamed via AirPlay from an iPhone, iPad, iPod touch, Apple TV, or Mac.

Touch Controls
A single tap plays or pauses music or Siri; a double-tap skips; a triple-tap skips back; touch and hold to activate Siri; tap or hold the + and - portion of the panel for volume up or down.

Wireless Connectivity
Direct guest access
Thread (only for HomeKit Thread devices)
Ultra Wideband chip for device proximity (with a U1-equipped iPhone; via a future firmware update)

Accessibility Features
Touch Accommodations
Siri
VoiceOver
Home app and HomeKit
Intercom transcriptions (via a future firmware update)

System Requirements
iPhone SE, iPhone 6s or later, or iPod touch (7th generation) with the latest iOS; or iPad Pro, iPad (5th generation or later), iPad Air 2 or later, or iPad mini 4 or later with the latest iPadOS
Wi-Fi 4 (802.11n) internet access

Environmental Requirements
32 to 95° operating temperature
5 to 90% non-condensing relative humidity
Operating altitude up to 10,000'

Compatibility
iPhone: iPhone 12 Pro Max, iPhone 12 Pro, iPhone 12, iPhone 12 mini, iPhone 11 Pro Max, iPhone 11 Pro, iPhone 11, iPhone XS Max, iPhone XS, iPhone XR, iPhone X, iPhone 8 Plus, iPhone 8, iPhone 7 Plus, iPhone 7, iPhone 6s Plus, iPhone 6s, iPhone SE (2nd generation), iPhone SE (1st generation)

iPad: 12.9" iPad Pro, 11" iPad Pro, 10.5" iPad Pro, 9.7" iPad Pro, iPad, 8th generation), iPad (7th generation), iPad (6th generation), iPad (5th generation), iPad Air (4th generation), iPad Air (3rd generation), iPad Air 2, iPad mini (5th generation), iPad mini 4

iPod touch: iPod touch (7th generation)

Name: Apple Magic Mouse 2 Space Gray
Short description:
• Wireless Bluetooth Connectivity
  • Optimized Foot Design
  • Mac Compatible
  • Built-In Rechargeable Battery
  • Lightning to USB Cable Included
Description: Eliminate the use of traditional batteries with the space gray Apple Magic Mouse 2. Featuring an updated design, the Magic Mouse 2 is lighter and has fewer moving parts, thanks to its continuous bottom shell and built-in rechargeable battery. The Magic Mouse 2 also has an optimized foot design, which tracks with ease and moves with less resistance across the surface of your desk. You can also use the Multi-Touch surface to perform gestures such as swiping between websites, opening the Notification or Mission Control, and scrolling through documents. Magic Mouse 2 can be used right out of the box and will pair automatically with your Mac.\n\nPlease note that the Magic Mouse 2 will work with a Bluetooth-enabled Mac computer with Mac OS X 10.11 or later..

Name: Apple TV 4K 32GB Black
Short description:
• Stream Multimedia Content Wirelessly
  • Apple AirPlay & iCloud Integration
  • HDR10 & Dolby Vision Support
  • 64-Bit A10X Fusion Chip
  • Siri Search/Multidirectional Navigation
  • Built-In Wi-Fi & Ethernet Connectivity
  • Supports up to 4K via HDMI
  • 32GB Storage Capacity
  • Rechargeable Siri Remote Control
  • Search Across Multiple Apps
Description:
Access a variety of streaming content in 4K HDR with the 32GB Apple TV 4K. With on-board iTunes and iCloud integration, the Apple TV 4K allows you seamlessly enjoy your existing library of music, photos, and videos. You can also explore additional content such TV shows, movies, and games thanks to the integrated App Store. With streaming apps like Netflix, Hulu, MLB, and HBO NOW, you can enjoy an array of multimedia content. Internet access is enabled by built-in 802.11ac Wi-Fi and Ethernet connectivity. Additionally, Apple AirPlay connectivity allows you to wirelessly mirror content from compatible Apple devices such as iPhones, iPads, and MacBooks.

The Apple TV 4K connects to your display via HDMI and supports resolutions up to UHD with support for the HDR10 and Dolby Vision HDR formats, as well as Dolby Atmos surround sound; an HDMI cable is available separately. The included rechargeable Siri Remote is equipped with a microphone that enables you to speak directly into the remote to quickly find the content you're looking for. The remote's touch surface is designed to offer intuitive, smartphone-like navigation. With its 3.9"-square footprint, the Apple TV 4K offers easy placement near your display. The included Lightning-to-USB cable will allow you to charge the remote control.

4K HDR Compatibility
4K gives you a crisper picture using four times more pixels than Full HD. High Dynamic Range (HDR) delivers brighter, more realistic colors and enhanced detail.

News and Sports Streaming Live
The Apple TV 4K offers live news and sports. You'll find your favorite sports from apps like NBA and MLB, and late-breaking news from apps like Bloomberg and CNN, helping to make it easy to watch the live programming you love.

The Apple TV App Consolidates Your Content
The Apple TV app lets you browse content from over 60 video services without switching from one app to the next. You'll find movies, shows, and handpicked recommendations. The Apple TV app is already on iPhone, iPad, and the Apple TV and is designed to work seamlessly across them all. So, if you stop watching in one place, you can start again later on a different device.

Watch Now
Watch Now serves up your favorite shows. It features Up Next, which lets you pick up where you left off, and What to Watch, where you'll find handpicked recommendations.

Library
Everything you've purchased from iTunes, along with your current rentals, shows up in your Apple TV app library. If an HD title in your library is released in 4K HDR, it automatically updates for free.

Store
The Store tab is where you'll find video services and the content they offer.

Search
Find movies and shows by entering a title or actor in the Search tab. Or ask Siri, no matter what you're looking for.

You Ask, and Siri Delivers
Ask Siri for a movie, show, genre, actor, or song you love. Siri is also helpful when you're not sure what you want. Just say something like, "Show me movies in 4K," and Siri delivers.

Designed for Enhanced Performance and Graphics
The A10X Fusion chip is engineered to provide a powerful platform for enjoying rich, interactive games and apps.

All Your Photos, Videos, and Music on Your Display
Enjoy photos and videos from your iCloud Photo Library (with your iCloud-enabled device) or shared albums on the big screen. Connect Apple Music to your home theater, and let your friends and family share their photos and videos with AirPlay.

Photos and Videos
Memories automatically creates collections of your photos and videos, and the Apple TV 4K lets you see them in 4K. If you create Live Photo loops or bounces on your iPhone, you can share those on the big screen as well.

Apple Music
Apple Music gives you access to over 40 million songs on your Apple TV, with a valid subscription. You can use it to power a party or just listen, explore, and discover great music with family and friends.

Share Photos, Presentations, Websites, and More
AirPlay allows you or your guests to wirelessly share whatever's on an iPhone, iPad, or Mac in big-screen fashion.

Control Your Smart Home Through the Apple TV 4K
Shut your garage door. Control your home's heat or air conditioning. Double-check the locks. The Apple TV 4K lets you use your iOS device to control HomeKit-enabled accessories remotely with the Home app.

Bluetooth Keyboard-Compatible
The Apple TV 4K is compatible with the Magic Keyboard and the 2011 Apple Wireless Keyboard.

Environmental Features
Both the Apple TV 4K and Siri Remote are BFR- and PVC-free. The Siri remote features arsenic-free glass and a recyclable aluminum enclosure, while the Apple TV 4K meets ENERGY STAR 5.0 requirements.

Accessibility
Accessibility features help people with disabilities get the most out of their Apple TV 4K. With built-in support for vision, hearing, physical and motor skills, and learning and literacy, you can find and enjoy your favorite entertainment.
VoiceOver
Zoom
Increase contrast
Reduce motion
Closed caption and SDH support
Audio descriptions
Siri and dictation
Switch control

Siri Remote Features
Bluetooth wireless technology
IR transmitter
Accelerometer and three-axis gyro
Lightning connector for charging
Rechargeable battery providing months of battery life on a single charge (with typical daily usage)

System Requirements
iTunes purchasing and renting and Home Sharing require iTunes Store account
Requires 802.11 wireless, Ethernet network, or broadband Internet access
Requires 4K and HDR TV for 4K and HDR streaming
HDMI cable

Name: Apple TV 4K 64GB Black
Short description:
• Stream Multimedia Content Wirelessly
  • Apple AirPlay & iCloud Integration
  • HDR10 & Dolby Vision Support
  • 64-Bit A10X Fusion Chip
  • Siri Search/Multidirectional Navigation
  • Built-In Wi-Fi & Ethernet Connectivity
  • Supports up to 4K via HDMI
  • 64GB Storage Capacity
  • Rechargeable Siri Remote Control
  • Search Across Multiple Apps
Description:
Access a variety of streaming content in 4K HDR with the 64GB Apple TV 4K. With on-board iTunes and iCloud integration, the Apple TV 4K allows you seamlessly enjoy your existing library of music, photos, and videos. You can also explore additional content such TV shows, movies, and games thanks to the integrated App Store. With streaming apps like Netflix, Hulu, MLB, and HBO NOW, you can enjoy an array of multimedia content. Internet access is enabled by built-in 802.11ac Wi-Fi and Ethernet connectivity. Additionally, Apple AirPlay connectivity allows you to wirelessly mirror content from compatible Apple devices such as iPhones, iPads, and MacBooks.

The Apple TV 4K connects to your display via HDMI and supports resolutions up to UHD with support for the HDR10 and Dolby Vision HDR formats, as well as Dolby Atmos surround sound; an HDMI cable is available separately. The included rechargeable Siri Remote is equipped with a microphone that enables you to speak directly into the remote to quickly find the content you're looking for. The remote's touch surface is designed to offer intuitive, smartphone-like navigation. With its 3.9"-square footprint, the Apple TV 4K offers easy placement near your display. The included Lightning-to-USB cable will allow you to charge the remote control.

4K HDR Compatibility
4K gives you a crisper picture using four times more pixels than Full HD. High Dynamic Range (HDR) delivers brighter, more realistic colors and enhanced detail.

News and Sports Streaming Live
The Apple TV 4K offers live news and sports. You'll find your favorite sports from apps like NBA and MLB, and late-breaking news from apps like Bloomberg and CNN, helping to make it easy to watch the live programming you love.

The Apple TV App Consolidates Your Content
The Apple TV app lets you browse content from over 60 video services without switching from one app to the next. You'll find movies, shows, and handpicked recommendations. The Apple TV app is already on iPhone, iPad, and the Apple TV and is designed to work seamlessly across them all. So, if you stop watching in one place, you can start again later on a different device.

Watch Now
Watch Now serves up your favorite shows. It features Up Next, which lets you pick up where you left off, and What to Watch, where you'll find handpicked recommendations.

Library
Everything you've purchased from iTunes, along with your current rentals, shows up in your Apple TV app library. If an HD title in your library is released in 4K HDR, it automatically updates for free.

Store
The Store tab is where you'll find video services and the content they offer.

Search
Find movies and shows by entering a title or actor in the Search tab. Or ask Siri, no matter what you're looking for.

You Ask, and Siri Delivers
Ask Siri for a movie, show, genre, actor, or song you love. Siri is also helpful when you're not sure what you want. Just say something like, "Show me movies in 4K," and Siri delivers.

Designed for Enhanced Performance and Graphics
The A10X Fusion chip is engineered to provide a powerful platform for enjoying rich, interactive games and apps.

All Your Photos, Videos, and Music on Your Display
Enjoy photos and videos from your iCloud Photo Library (with your iCloud-enabled device) or shared albums on the big screen. Connect Apple Music to your home theater, and let your friends and family share their photos and videos with AirPlay.

Photos and Videos
Memories automatically creates collections of your photos and videos, and the Apple TV 4K lets you see them in 4K. If you create Live Photo loops or bounces on your iPhone, you can share those on the big screen as well.

Apple Music
Apple Music gives you access to over 40 million songs on your Apple TV, with a valid subscription. You can use it to power a party or just listen, explore, and discover great music with family and friends.

Share Photos, Presentations, Websites, and More
AirPlay allows you or your guests to wirelessly share whatever's on an iPhone, iPad, or Mac in big-screen fashion.

Control Your Smart Home Through the Apple TV 4K
Shut your garage door. Control your home's heat or air conditioning. Double-check the locks. The Apple TV 4K lets you use your iOS device to control HomeKit-enabled accessories remotely with the Home app.

Bluetooth Keyboard-Compatible
The Apple TV 4K is compatible with the Magic Keyboard and the 2011 Apple Wireless Keyboard.

Environmental Features
Both the Apple TV 4K and Siri Remote are BFR- and PVC-free. The Siri remote features arsenic-free glass and a recyclable aluminum enclosure, while the Apple TV 4K meets ENERGY STAR 5.0 requirements.

Accessibility
Accessibility features help people with disabilities get the most out of their Apple TV 4K. With built-in support for vision, hearing, physical and motor skills, and learning and literacy, you can find and enjoy your favorite entertainment.
VoiceOver
Zoom
Increase contrast
Reduce motion
Closed caption and SDH support
Audio descriptions
Siri and dictation
Switch control

Siri Remote Features
Bluetooth wireless technology
IR transmitter
Accelerometer and three-axis gyro
Lightning connector for charging
Rechargeable battery providing months of battery life on a single charge (with typical daily usage)

System Requirements
iTunes purchasing and renting and Home Sharing require iTunes Store account
Requires 802.11 wireless, Ethernet network, or broadband Internet access
Requires 4K and HDR TV for 4K and HDR streaming
HDMI cable
Categories: Consumer Electronics, Consumer Electronics > TV & Streaming

Name: Apple Watch Magnetic Charger to USB 2M White
Description: We wanted to make charging your Apple Watch utterly effortless. So we arrived at a solution that combines our MagSafe technology with inductive charging. Its a completely sealed system free of exposed contacts. And its very forgiving, requiring no precise alignment. You simply hold the connector near the back of the watch, where magnets cause it to snap into place automatically.

Name: Azzaro Visit POUR HOMME EDT, 100ml‏
Description: Visit by Azzaro is a woody and spicy Eau de Toilette for modern, cosmopolitan men who enjoy the exciting city lifestyle. The captivating opening of the fragrance is intense with nutmeg tones, accentuated by the scent of cardamom, a hint of pink pepper and a blast of ginger. The spicy opening fades in favor of a sweet heart composed of warm Lebanese cedar, woody incense and masculine guaiac tree. The scent settles in an oriental blend of gray amber and musk. Visit is a unique sexy fragrance; ideal for wintertime and nightwear.

Name: Azaro Chrome Legend Eau De Toilette Spray 125ml‏
Description: Azzaro Chrome Legend is an aromatic fruity fragrance for men. This fresh and cool scent is perfect for the modern man. The fragrance opens fresh and pleasant with green apple and a blast of orange and tea giving an exquisite vibe. The heart notes are magical with soft musk and a hint of cedar. Tonka bean and amber give a sweet vibe to the heart while vetiver and oakmoss surround it with spiciness. The dry-down is delightful with amber. Azzaro Chrome Legend is a refreshing and uplifting fragrance that is ideal for daywear and summertime.

Name: AZZARO pour homme ELIXIR EDT 100ml
Description:
An oriental fragrance for men was launched in 2009. It comes in an elegant red bottle. The perfume contains a mixture of natural ingredients such as bergamot, lavender, geranium, oak moss, coumarin, tonka bean, vanilla and many other distinct ingredients that give you an attrctive and refreshing scent that lasts for a long time with you.

About the brand:

Azzaro is a premium brand for the finest and finest perfumes, its fragrances are distinguished by elegance and high quality, created in the image of its founder, Loris Azzaro. Sicilian by birth, the designer quickly gained fame in the late 1960s for his glamorous and sexy outfits. The brand has expanded to include perfumes, introducing Azzaro perfume for women in 1975, since its inception and it continues to release the latest perfumes under the supervision of the current artistic director Vanessa Seward.

Name: Bentley by Bentley EDT Spray FOR MEN 100ML
Bentley Azure For Men  EDT Spray 100ML
Description: Refresh yourself with a scent that’s crisp and invigorating with Bentley Azure, a stunning men’s cologne. This aromatic and citrusy sweet blend can inspire visions of a great adventure outdoors, preparing you with a sensual aroma all day and into the night. Top notes of citrusy bergamot, tangerine, and pineapple awaken the senses while delicate violet leaf brings them down for a lighter caress. Middle notes of clary sage, tea and lavender continue to soothe the mind and body, though the inclusion of paprika adds a bit of spicy flair. Bottom notes of sweet tonka bean and cashmere wood balance the bold ingredients with their moderate yet enticing aromas.

Name: Giorgio YELLOW BY Beverly Hills for Men EDT SPRAY 118ML
Description: Giorgio Beverly Hills, From its first glimmer until the last sigh, Giorgio cologne launched in 1984 is one Oriental blend for men that manages to delight and inspire. The opening is friendly orange and fruity notes with just a hint of a pout from a splash of aldehydic bergamot. The core borders on the exotic with woodsy sandalwood and cedar partnering with spicy cinnamon and patchouli to host a beautiful floral dance of warm carnation, orris root and rose. The base is a pure magnetic attraction as the goodness of amber and oakmoss is layered in irresistible honey and vanilla, topped with tonka bean and bound with musk. Rich, fulfilling silage sparks the imagination as it lingers and entwines.

Name: G By Beverly Hills FOR WOMEN EDP Spray 90ml
Description:
• Giorgio Beverly Hills G Eau de Parfum spray was first introduced to the house of Giorgio in 1981. In May 2012, an updated version of this classic scent was introduced in the form of Giorgio Beverly Hills G which is a light and summery interpretation of the original fragrance.
  • Giorgio Beverly Hills G boasts notes of orange blossom, bergamot, jasmine and gardenia which fuse together to create a rich, floral cocktail that celebrates the rich and luxurious lifestyle of California.
  • Giorgio Beverly Hills G Eau de Parfum spray is a classic fragrance which is housed in an equally classic bottle; perfect for any occasion.
